---
title: Jello Loader | Full Page Loading Screen
notes: This example demonstrates the use of jello loader as a full page transition. For example, Rosetta's loading screen as games are being scheduled by Fanapp and sent back to TeamSnap.
layout: demo
---

<div class="main-container">

  <h1>{{title}}</h1>

  <div class="Loader Loader--jello Loader--fixedCenter">

    <div class="Loader-indicator">

      <span class="JelloAnimation">
        <span class="JelloAnimation-shadow"></span>
        <span class="JelloAnimation-box"></span>
      </span>

      <div class="Loader-indicatorText">Scheduling Games..</div>

    </div>

    <hr class="Divider Divider--indented" />

    <div class="Loader-message">Nice Shirt! Is that Velour?</div>

  </div>

</div>
